      "content": "i tried the warm bath and everything but it didn't even touch the pain. im basically sitting here crying lol. is it really that dangerous to just take an extra 400 or 800 of the ibuprofen? i feel like if i can just get past this peak of pain i'll be fine. i just need to know if it's actually safe to take a higher dose if the standard one isnt working.",
